name: Buildings & Peonies
description:
I explore neural networks capabilities to generate art. My inputs guide the networks to generate the curated outcomes. 

« Buildings & Peonies » is one of the outcome I selected while I was exploring what could come out from my main obsessions : rose gold (the color but also the metal) and the photographic printing process called « cyanotype » that produces a cyan-blue print.
